Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Layer:11 INFORNOGRAPHY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你來的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不必要在這
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很累了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.51,0:06:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看見這東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巖倉玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟網上的玲音是同一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經在網上見過你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘綜合研究所的生化學基礎研究團隊成功地\N分析出染色體分子構造…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（玲音是偷窺者）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我才是真正的玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這真實的世界你已經沒有存在的價值了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自殺了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？ 為何你要存在？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何要我去感覺你的存在？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯 我就是網上的神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音多和大家接觸比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的變了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近你又變回原樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧？ 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我們不好 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很累嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我累了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然自己直接接駁計算機登入
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一併讀取所有數據是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在的狀況已經超過了你的界線
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是機械吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把我說成是機械一般
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.91,0:13:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒有這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只不過是軟體的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 其實你只是個軟體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.71,0:13:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是硬體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軟體？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是個執行程序 有肉體的軟體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.92,0:13:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千砂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千砂 你記得我們曾一起回家？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於明白了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你所說的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死是非常容易的 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要死並不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很簡單的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 你已經有了死亡的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.23,0:15:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要解除手槍的保險制
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:15:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對準目標
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用雙手扼緊 再有姆指按制開關
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.71,0:16:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生的力量就夠用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣 你還留戀現實世界嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡滑了 是你叫我來這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒有找過你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有肉體是沒有意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這說法不對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們明天放學後大家集合見面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那男的真帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞莉絲 關於你和老師的謠言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你找到了男朋友交往 那謠言就會不攻自破
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:17:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們明天再聊吧 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那事情是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰…誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…你會變成這個…樣子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:17:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個並不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有偷看亞莉絲的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更沒有把秘密放在網上 我真的沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玲音 一定是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我親眼目睹玲音偷看的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎不只有一個我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是另一個我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞莉絲也可能不只一人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最多只能說不是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要讓那件事就像沒發生過的消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經不需要任何道具了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:19:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網絡現實世界的分界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經被破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經可以隨意進入網絡界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是我出現在這裡的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於那個謠言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定能使它變成不曾發生過的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恐怖 太恐怖了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.11,0:19:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞莉絲 早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼無精打采？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道月經來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是不知羞恥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茱莉 今天我心情不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天收到一個很下流的電子郵件…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你撒謊 昨天我們還…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.51,0:20:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得今天你好像有點不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個老師很帥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有傳言說他跟某高中三年級女生交往
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.53,0:20:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:21:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師和我的事不就沒有發生過？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.63,0:21:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟那老師有什麼關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你也喜歡那位老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行 你已經太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是 他已經有女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.94,0:21:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 說話也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.01,0:21:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 早
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.51,0:21:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 快過來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.01,0:21:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一點 快一點 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.41,0:22:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 她在笑
